<h2 id="task">Task</h2>

<p><a href="#task-object">Task Object</a> </p>

<h3 id="create-task">Create Task</h3>
<pre class="highlight http"><code><span class="nf">POST</span>   <span class="nn">api/projects/{project_id}/taskgroups/{task_group_id}/tasks</span> <span class="k">HTTP</span><span class="o">/</span><span class="m">1.1</span>
<span class="na">Accept</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="s">application/json</span>
<span class="na">Authorization</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="s">Token "YOUR ACCESS TOKEN"</span>

HTTP/1.1 200 OK
Content-Type: application/json
</code></pre>
<pre class="highlight plaintext"><code>Sample Request
</code></pre>
<pre class="highlight json"><code><span class="p">{</span><span class="w">
    </span><span class="nt">"name"</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="s2">"Important - Monitoring Third-party Services"</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w">
    </span><span class="nt">"taskgroup_id"</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="mi">901</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w">
    </span><span class="nt">"due_date"</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="s2">"2016-07-29"</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w">
    </span><span class="nt">"assigned_to"</span><span class="p">:{</span><span class="nt">"id"</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="mi">273</span><span class="p">},</span><span class="w">
    </span><span class="nt">"attachment"</span><span class="p">:[</span><span class="mi">3781</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="p">}</span><span class="w">
</span></code></pre>

<aside>POST  api/projects/{project_id}/taskgroups/{task_group_id}/tasks</aside>

<h3 id="retrieve-task">Retrieve Task</h3>
<pre class="highlight http"><code><span class="nf">GET</span>  <span class="nn">api/projects/{project_id}/taskgroups/{task_group_id}/tasks/{task_id}</span> <span class="k">HTTP</span><span class="o">/</span><span class="m">1.1</span>
<span class="na">Accept</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="s">application/json</span>
<span class="na">Authorization</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="s">Token "YOUR ACCESS TOKEN"</span>

HTTP/1.1 200 OK
Content-Type: application/json
</code></pre>

<aside>GET   api/projects/{project_id}/taskgroups/{task_group_id}/tasks/{task_id}</aside>

<h4 id="returns">Returns</h4>

<p>If the call succeeds, the <a href="#task-object">task object</a> will be returned.</p>

<h3 id="update-task">Update Task</h3>
<pre class="highlight http"><code><span class="nf">PATCH</span>  <span class="nn">api/projects/{project_id}/taskgroups/{task_group_id}/tasks/{task_id}</span> <span class="k">HTTP</span><span class="o">/</span><span class="m">1.1</span>
<span class="na">Accept</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="s">application/json</span>
<span class="na">Authorization</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="s">Token "YOUR ACCESS TOKEN"</span>

HTTP/1.1 200 OK
Content-Type: application/json
</code></pre>
<pre class="highlight json"><code><span class="p">{</span><span class="w">
    </span><span class="nt">"name"</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="s2">"Important - Monitoring Third-party Services"</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w">
    </span><span class="nt">"assigned_to"</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w">
        </span><span class="p">{</span><span class="w">
            </span><span class="nt">"id"</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="mi">273</span><span class="w">
        </span><span class="p">},</span><span class="w">
    </span><span class="nt">"due_date"</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="s2">"2016-07-29"</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w">
    </span><span class="nt">"attachment"</span><span class="p">:[</span><span class="mi">3781</span><span class="p">],</span><span class="w">
    </span><span class="nt">"estimate"</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="p">}</span><span class="w">
</span></code></pre>

<aside>PATCH  api/projects/{project_id}/taskgroups/{task_group_id}/tasks/{task_id}</aside>

<h4 id="returns">Returns</h4>

<p>If call succeeds, the <a href="#task-object">task object</a> will be returned.</p>

